Theuns du Toit urinating on a black student’s belongings. Image: Times Live screenshot from video of incident By Andile Mngxitama On Saturday 14 May 2022 white Stellenbosch University student, Theuns du Toit, was recorded on video peeing on the books, desk and laptop of a black student, Babalo Ndwayana, after forcibly gaining entry into his room at the campus residence. Here’s a short lesson on what is racism 101 in response to this peeing incident. Let’s learn together… What is racism 101? Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF) – a radical black consciousness organization – and the author of the essay BLACKS CAN’T BE RACIST. When using any of Black Opinion’s content, partly or in full, kindly always provide an active hyperlink to the original material.